{"url": "http://www.justjared.com/2018/02/12/lupita-nyongo-recalls-the-time-she-shaved-her-head/", "text": "Lupita Nyong\u2019o is on the cover of Allure magazine\u2019s Culture of Hair issue, on national newsstands on February 20.\n\nHere\u2019s what the Black Panther star had to share with the magazine:\n\nOn shaving her head as a teenager: \u201cI went into the hair salon, and I said, \u2018Let\u2019s cut it off.\u2019 It was almost a dare to myself: Can I live without hair? He shaved it right off. It was so scary but so liberating because I went completely bald.\u201d\n\nOn the language of hair: \u201cI like the term \u2018kinky.\u2019 Some people don\u2019t like that term, but when I think about my hair, I think of it as African kinky hair.\u201d\n\nOn fame: \u201cWhat fame does is there is an illusion of familiarity that is cast into the world. So it\u2019s about negotiating with that illusion because oftentimes you encounter people who have encountered you, but you haven\u2019t encountered them. It\u2019s a little weird to find your footing. I have to be aware of that possibility, not imprisoned by it. It\u2019s like, how do I find freedom within that awareness?\u201d\n\nFor more from Lupita, visit Allure.com.", "images": ["http://cdn02.cdn.justjared.com/wp-content/uploads/sidebar/jjjr_logo_featured.gif", "http://cdn04.cdn.justjared.com/wp-content/themes/default/images/toofab_footer2.gif", "http://cdn03.cdn.justjared.com/wp-content/themes/default/images/button_feed.gif", "http://cdn02.cdn.justjared.com/wp-content/themes/default/images/jj-circle-logo.gif", "http://cdn02.cdn.justjared.com/wp-content/uploads/headlines/2018/02/lupita-nyongo-allure.jpg", "http://cdn04.cdn.justjared.com/wp-content/themes/default/images/justjared_circlelogo_2.gif", "http://cdn01.cdn.justjared.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nyongo-allure/thumbs/lupita-nyongo-allure-01.jpg", "http://cdn02.cdn.justjaredjr.com/wp-content/uploads/headlines/2020/04/tisdale-hudgens-bloopers-singalong-video